{"type":null,"faqId":33377,"title":"手机的截屏(截图)方式有哪些？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">常用的截屏（截图）方式4种</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">智能截屏：使用指关节双击截取全屏或绘制封闭图案截取所选屏幕。设置路径“设置-&gt;智能辅助-&gt;更多-&gt;智能截屏”打开。使用时在要截取的屏幕，指关节用稍力敲击屏幕2下，或者用稍力敲击一下后不抬起，绘制封闭图案。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=105459\" style=\"width:1.7618055in;height:3.1333334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">按键截屏：非待机状态下，进入要截屏的界面，同时按住音量下键和电源键2秒，可以截屏；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">按钮截屏：非待机状态下，进入要截屏的界面，下拉状态栏选择截屏图标进行截屏。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=105460\" style=\"width:2.073611in;height:3.45625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>荣耀智灵键快速截屏：进入“设置-智能辅助-智灵”，定义单击/双击/长按的快捷操作为截屏，则任意屏幕下操作荣耀智灵键对用动作可实现截屏。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=105461\" style=\"width:2.073611in;height:3.6861112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":2,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8079","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748591000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":168,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"怎么截图,都有哪些方法","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}